{
  "texts": [
    "Despite their popularity, DL models have a major disadvantage when it comes to policy extraction.",
    "Specifically, the resulting models are so complex that operate as black boxes.",
    "This makes them non-transparent and essentially impossible to understand by any human.",
    "The rising popularity of DL has driven a need to explain and interpret the workings and decisions made by ANN trained classifiers.",
    "There is a subtle but important difference in the semantics of the words \"explainable\" and \"interpretable.\""
  ]
}